<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="aboutCard">
            <p class="text-center">
                Imperium is a 2-player deckbuilding video game that focuses on delivering a gameplay experience similar to that of a Trading Card Game.

                In Imperium, both players use their heroes to buy and summon minions, which are used to attack each other. The minions available for recruiting are randomized at the start of every game, requiring players to adopt new strategies and tactics in order to overcome their opponents!

                Lastly, the game also features leveling up for your hero! Quest cards increase your hero's experience, which can then be used to unlock powerful abilities!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

